Ariel X is undefeated this season and has been instrumental in training new wrestlers. As a teacher and leader, Ariel is one of the best at US. Winter Sky is a local girl who wanted to see if US is real wrestling. She found the hard way. It is. Winter's best offensive weapon is her looks. Beyond that, she will need some serious mat time. One thing that surprised me was her spirit. She never gave up and she fought to the end. That is all we ask of our girls. We don't care if you suck, but we want you to try. Winter brought it. Then Ariel took it and fucked her with it but that's not the point..
title: Ariel "The Assassin" X (4-0)
